<div id="review_962580117" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/962580117" />
    <a title="Joey Woolfardis" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4639825-joey-woolfardis"><img alt="Joey Woolfardis" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1490696206p2/4639825.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/962580117?book_show_action=true">Jun 09, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Joey Woolfardis" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Joey Woolfardis" href="/user/show/4639825-joey-woolfardis">Joey Woolfardis</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4639825-joey-woolfardis?shelf=ce20">ce20</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4639825-joey-woolfardis?shelf=2014">2014</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4639825-joey-woolfardis?shelf=bookshelf">bookshelf</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4639825-joey-woolfardis?shelf=intriguing-but-ultimately-naff">intriguing-but-ultimately-naff</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4639825-joey-woolfardis?shelf=feminine">feminine</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4639825-joey-woolfardis?shelf=sterling">sterling</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4639825-joey-woolfardis?shelf=illustrated">illustrated</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4639825-joey-woolfardis?shelf=bairns">bairns</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4639825-joey-woolfardis?shelf=childhood">childhood</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer962580117&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer962580117" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17237400970307809843">I assume that this is where my love for staircases came from. A mildly impressionable child would not hesitate to revel in the fact that, unlike almost all other books I&apos;ve known, the secret staircase remains a secret with the children.</span>
  <span id="freeText17237400970307809843" style="display:none">I assume that this is where my love for staircases came from. A mildly impressionable child would not hesitate to revel in the fact that, unlike almost all other books I've known, the secret staircase remains a secret with the children.</span>
